main event: A private citizen observed an unidentified flying object with a half-oval, half-circular shape in Iceland on 6 Aug 55.
interesting points: The object changed formation from a steady line to scattered and back to a straight line,The object was brown-gray and about the size of a DC-3 airplane,It was traveling in a northwesterly direction at an estimated speed of 700 knots,The radar was out of operation at the time of the sighting,The observer concluded the object was not a natural phenomenon.
